institute for computational and mathematical engineering remembrances in celebration of gene golub icme logo intranet remembrances in celebration of gene golub friday february 29 2008 from 2 pm to 5 pm videos of speakers at gene's remembrances event on february 29 2008 the gene golub fellowship fund gene in his contemplative pose old union ballroom stanford university stanford ca dear friends of gene's old union at stanford we d like to invite you to the remembrances in celebration of gene golub meeting on february 29 2008 which would have been gene's 76 th birthday the memorial meeting will be held in the ballroom of the newly renovated old union on stanford campus beginning at 2 pm the program for the remembrances event is available at remebrances program the meeting will start with remembrances by several of gene's many close friends to date we are so pleased to have confirmation from celia concus leah friedman walter gander alvin golub gene's brother marvin knopp jill knuth victor pereyra michael saunders and werner stuetzle after the organized speakers who will share many wonderful stories of gene we will have an open mike session where you will have the opportunity to speak for a couple of minutes if you so desire drinks and especially tasty snacks as gene would have liked it will be served throughout the meeting the symposium on gene golub's legacy will be held in honor of gene on march 1 the day after the memorial celebration information about the symposium can be found at symposium on gene golub's legacy if you plan to attend please register for the remembrances event at registration form this allows us to make an estimate of the expected number attending and also to create name badges before the event if you would like to speak during the open mike session please indicate that on the registration form also finally we would like to display a large collection of photos showing gene through the years if you have photos of gene that you would like to share please send a digital copy by email to margot with very best wishes from the 2 29 organizing committee leah friedman jim lambers walter murray margot gerritsen leahff stanford edu lambers stanford edu walter stanford edu margot gerritsen stanford edu detailed walking directions on campus if you walk from the bookstore and white plaza fountain toward the old union you ll see a building on the left labeled clubhouse it's part of the old union complex but is detached from the main building we will be in the clubhouse ballroom half a floor above ground level from 2 pm to 5 pm local hotel information is available at hotels view larger map the website for the event remembering gene golub around the world is located at http cs nyu edu overton genearoundtheworld view larger map gene's obituary in the stanford report is located at http news service stanford edu news 2007 november28 golub 112807 html the gene h golub memorial blog appears at http genehgolub blogspot com please contact mayita romero if you have any questions 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved icme home about icme people faculty staff students master of science directory doctor of philosophy directory gallery alumni ms alumni directory ph d alumni directory keeping in touch advisors prospective students admissions requirements deadlines application financing academics academic programs master of science doctor of philosophy mathematical and computational science courses current undergraduate service graduate service graduate core classx consulting c2 research research profiles theses icme theses sccm theses seminars list of seminars resources computer resources icme life history interactive timeline faculty pioneers in science computing george forsythe gene golub joe oliger sccm ms and phd programs sccm alumni lectures on the history of numerical analysis conferences mmds june 08 gene golub's legacy 03 08 remembering gene golub 02 08 stanford50 05 07 mmds 06 06 svg 01 04 contact us
